T1  - From Blackwell Dominance in Large Samples to Rényi Divergences and Back Again
AU  - Mu, Xiaosheng
AU  - Pomatto, Luciano
AU  - Strack, Philipp
AU  - Tamuz, Omer
Y1  - 2021/01/01
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/01/01
